{"tid":788992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港六成年輕人支持台灣獨立，半數人指一國兩制當地不適用","createTime":"2018-08-22T02:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T00:58:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8f93ffec8699a9c95d2fb61845f00a82b6282f","tid":788992,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180821/large/1534840591_6a81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180821%2Flarge%2F1534840591_6a81.jpg&h=0d47174d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">調查發現，香港人對台灣重新加入聯合國的最新贊成淨值，比半年前上升，達正30個百分點。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n港大民研計劃調查發現，54%受訪的港人反對台灣獨立，贊成者則佔34%，比率與半年前相約，但18至29歲年齡群組中，6成受訪者贊成台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，3成反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其餘表示「唔知/難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。深入分析顯示，年紀較大的巿民較反對台灣及西藏獨立，而受訪的港人對兩岸統一的信心繼續表示悲觀，最新淨值為負22個百分點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180821/58590086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58590086&d=Bww1wnCBjfkroq22lFLcxNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=322f33c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58590086&h=609491ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180821/58590086</a>"},{"pid":"d3d0e03e7f5f54ce1568f18a41fa0acddec0d01e","tid":788992,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"港大民研在2018年8月6至9日，透過真實訪員以隨機抽樣方式，成功以電話訪問1,000名香港巿民，發現反對台灣獨立的港人繼續比贊成獨立的多，最新贊成淨值為負20個百分點；35%受訪的港人認為「一國兩制」適用於台灣地區，認為不適用的佔50%，適用淨值為負14個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，港人對台灣重新加入聯合國的最新贊成淨值，比半年前上升，達正30個百分點，是1993年8月以來的新高。港大民研指出，整體而言，港人雖然反對台獨，但就繼續贊成給予台灣更大的國際空間。至於西藏問題方面，63%受訪的港人反對西藏獨立，贊成者佔19%，贊成淨值為負44個百分點。"},{"pid":"9fbc0538e717411ca098349848061ff5f39e41fb","tid":788992,"uid":143241,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"台灣本來就係獨立國家,個名叫中華民國！"},{"pid":"81e8495dd57389cba031ca83555c5f15d6feb13a","tid":788992,"uid":179266,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"其實個班唔知難講係咪尻尻地 咁大個人都冇立場？<br />\n定政治冷感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對個推又唔知入面幾多新移民唔識歷史而盲撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d9d39f0ac87332f78752e1976beb3482d76a17","tid":788992,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81e8495dd57389cba031ca83555c5f15d6feb13a","tid":788992,"uid":179266,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"其實個班唔知難講係咪尻尻地 咁大個人都冇立場？<br />\n定政治冷感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對個推又唔知入面幾多新移民唔識歷史而盲撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"個推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f370df08450ea99949bb3d37e6c51855a8122a","tid":788992,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"個三成真係on 撚79<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acad7578ea15418eb461a4d03b3816895540cda","tid":788992,"uid":1886,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9fbc0538e717411ca098349848061ff5f39e41fb","tid":788992,"uid":143241,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"